* 1N4007 — general-purpose silicon rectifier diode.
*
* Standard 1000V / 1A power rectifier — most common 50/60 Hz mains
* diode. SPICE-параметры — typical Si rectifier из Duncan's library
* (duncanamps.com), сопоставимо с datasheet ON Semi / Vishay.
*
* subcategory: rectifier
* Pins:
*   A — anode (anode), K — cathode (cathode).
.SUBCKT 1N4007 A K
D1 A K D_1N4007
.MODEL D_1N4007 D(Is=14.11n N=1.984 Rs=33.89m Cjo=51.17p M=0.5 Bv=1000 Ibv=10u Tt=4.32u)
.ENDS 1N4007
